name: DL-10
details:
Digital DelayThe digital delay of the IBANEZ DL10, in addition to covering a delay time range of 70 msec to 400 msec for doubling, repeat echoes and other effects, uses stereo outputs (two JRC4558D op-amps) to achieve a uniquely clear stereo echo signal.
produced: 1988 - 1993
9V, ??MA.
